def has_bowl_or_plate():
    # Function to check if there are bowls or plates within an observable area
    symbol has_bowl_or_plate=exists o: item : (is_bowl(o) or is_plate(o))
    return has_bowl_or_plate

behavior locate_bowls_or_plates():
    body:
        if not has_bowl_or_plate():
            # If there is no known bowl or plate, explore the area to locate one
            foreach o: item:
                if is_bowl(o) or is_plate(o) and not visited(o):
                    observe(o, "Check location of bowls and plates")
